Allow Only Rules
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
inbound rules
	src: (*) dst: (group = Web) conn: All Connections
	src: (group = Web) dst: (group = App) conn: All Connections
	src: (group = App) dst: (group = DB) conn: All Connections
outbound rules
	src: (*) dst: (group = Web) conn: All Connections
	src: (group = Web) dst: (group = App) conn: All Connections
	src: (group = App) dst: (group = DB) conn: All Connections